#: _posts/2024-12-12-quarkus-newsletter-51.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "\"Quarkus has surpassed the 1,000 contributor milestone\" by Dimitrios Andreadis will explore the evolution and future of Quarkus, Red Hat’s next-generation Java framework designed to optimize applications for cloud-native environments. \"Java Quarkus LangChain4j – Building a Chatbot\" by Bhagvan Kommadi will guide you through leveraging two powerful tools — Quarkus and LangChain4j — to create chatbots that are not only efficient and scalable but also capable of understanding and generating human-like responses. \"Testing Apache Camel Routes with Testcontainers\" by Andras Fejes describes how Apache Camel and Testcontainers combine EIPs for integration and Testcontainers for robust, automated testing. Hamid Khanjani's \"Hibernate Reactive with Panache: The Quarkus-Powered ORM Revolution for Reactive Java Applications and Kubernetes\" describes how when Hibernate is combined with Panache, an intuitive and declarative ORM layer from Quarkus, it becomes a game-changer for Java developers. Explore different choices available for developing a new Quarkus application in \"Getting Started with Quarkus: A Guide to Application Creation\" by Jagnya Datta Panigrahi."
msgstr "\"Quarkus has surpassed the 1,000 contributor milestone\", de Dimitrios Andreadis, explorará a evolução e o futuro do Quarkus, a estrutura Java de próxima geração da Red Hat projetada para otimizar aplicativos para ambientes nativos da nuvem. \"Java Quarkus LangChain4j - Construindo um Chatbot\", de Bhagvan Kommadi, guiará o senhor no aproveitamento de duas ferramentas poderosas - Quarkus e LangChain4j - para criar chatbots que não são apenas eficientes e escaláveis, mas também capazes de compreender e gerar respostas semelhantes às humanas. \"Testing Apache Camel Routes with Testcontainers\", de Andras Fejes, descreve como o Apache Camel e o Testcontainers combinam EIPs para integração e Testcontainers para testes robustos e automatizados. Hamid Khanjani, \"Hibernate Reactive with Panache: The Quarkus-Powered ORM Revolution for Reactive Java Applications and Kubernetes\" descreve como, quando o Hibernate é combinado com o Panache, uma camada ORM intuitiva e declarativa do Quarkus, ele se torna um divisor de águas para os desenvolvedores Java. Explore as diferentes opções disponíveis para desenvolver um novo aplicativo Quarkus em \"Getting Started with Quarkus: A Guide to Application Creation\", de Jagnya Datta Panigrahi."

